Ignore files

There are following configuration options to set up ignore lists on per-file basis:

  1. skipPreserveLineWidthList - a list of files or directories to disable preserving line width of.

  2. skipReplaceColorsList - a list of files or directories to disable color replacements of.

  3. skipTransformsList - a list of files to skip while transforming (applies to any transformation except SVGO).

  4. skipFilesList - a list of files to skip loading of. Files will be passed to another loader.
